    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在“恐怖故事”中 - 将其加入心愿单，并随着频繁更新将这款游戏打造成一次独特、令人恐惧和惊险的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/8c7b43df583ce1313133f3819187f821.poster.avif?t=1753150893\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/8c7b43df583ce1313133f3819187f821.webm?t=1753150893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/8c7b43df583ce1313133f3819187f821.mp4?t=1753150893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与“恐怖故事”一同踏上一段难忘的未知之旅！准备好迎接一个引人入胜的PVE体验，它不仅挑战恐惧的界限，还邀请你与朋友分享在一个沉浸式的合作冒险中带来的刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/7fd46407f66012afae979450ecd3909d.poster.avif?t=1753150893\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/7fd46407f66012afae979450ecd3909d.webm?t=1753150893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/7fd46407f66012afae979450ecd3909d.mp4?t=1753150893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥 <strong>合作恐怖：</strong> 与朋友组队进行心跳加速的4人合作游戏。共同面对恐怖，或者如果你敢的话，独自冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧟‍♂️ <strong>怪物爆发：</strong> 探索一座被噩梦般爆发笼罩的荒废科研设施。面对突变的恐怖，解开谜团，生存无情的袭击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕵️ <strong>单人生存：</strong> 对于那些更愿意独自一人行动的勇敢灵魂，单人游戏提供独特而紧张的生存体验。你能穿越扭曲的走廊，揭示黑暗的秘密吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌐 <strong>揭开未知：</strong> 沉浸在一个充满叙事的恐怖冒险中，挑战你的智慧和生存本能。揭示被腐化设施中隐藏的秘密，面对潜伏在阴影中的恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好面对等待的噩梦了吗？鼓起勇气，组建你的团队，或者独自勇闯黑暗。《恐怖故事》在等待着你，恐惧已经进化。你能在SRF实验室中生存下来吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/bac736116eaf3e0847f21a9d457c9eac.poster.avif?t=1753150893\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/bac736116eaf3e0847f21a9d457c9eac.webm?t=1753150893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/bac736116eaf3e0847f21a9d457c9eac.mp4?t=1753150893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
